\"from\": 712, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"a drugs test\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris Olympics 2024 While Pan was not named in the investigation, 11 of the 23 athletes who had failed tests are competing in the French capital this summer.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.7593829345658994, \"rank\": 0.3031820617678658, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 820}, {\"ngram\": \"Pan\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the investigation\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"the 23 athletes\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"failed tests\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, after Wednesday's race, former Australian swimmer Hawke - who featured at the 2000 and 2004 Olympic Games - took to Instagram to voice his 'anger' over the swim, which he argued was 'not real'.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9926431493670889, \"rank\": 0.005353802785634802, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hawke\", \"score\": 0.9911907342345835, \"rank\": 0.008709771412127313, \"text\": \"Hawke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hawke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hawke\"}, {\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.231039042715417e-23, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wednesday's race\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2000 and 2004 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"his 'anger\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the swim\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Listen, I am just gonna be honest.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am angry at that swim.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that swim\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am angry for a number of reasons,' an irate Hawke told his followers in a video.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hawke\", \"score\": 0.9911907342345835, \"rank\": 0.008709771412127313, \"text\": \"Hawke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hawke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hawke\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"reasons\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"his followers\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Look, my friends are the fastest swimmers in history, from Rowdy Gaines to Alex Popov to Gary Hall Jr to Anthony Irvin to King Kyle Chalmers.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rowdy Gaines\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\"}, {\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Popov_(architect)\", \"score\": 0.9999936068834083, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Popov\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q42973\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Popov_(architect)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Popov_(architect)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest swimmers\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"Gary Hall Jr\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"Anthony Irvin\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"King Kyle Chalmers\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know these people intimately, I have studied them for 30 years.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these people\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"30 years\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have studied this sport, I have studied speed.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I understand it, I am an expert in it.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an expert\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what I do, okay?\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'And I am upset right now because you do not win a 100m freestyle by a body length on that field.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 100m freestyle\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1704}, {\"ngram\": \"a body length\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1721}, {\"ngram\": \"that field\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You just do not do it.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not humanly possible to beat that field by a body length, okay?\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that field\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"a body length\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not.'\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hawke continued: 'So I do not care what you say\\u2026 this is not a race thing, this is not against any one particular person or any nation.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hawke\", \"score\": 0.9911907342345835, \"rank\": 0.008709771412127313, \"text\": \"Hawke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hawke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hawke\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a race thing\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"any one particular person\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"any nation\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is just what I see and what I know.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'These are my friends, these are the people I have studied, this is the work that I have put in for 30 years, I understand it.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"30 years\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not real.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not beat that field.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that field\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kyle Chalmers, David Popovici, Jack Alexy?\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2192, \"end\": 2205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kyle Chalmers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\"}, {\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chalmers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chalmers, David\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chalmers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chalmers\"}, {\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chalmers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chalmers, David\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chalmers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chalmers\"}, {\"begin\": 2223, \"end\": 2227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.9592474817778839, \"rank\": 0.03655109133597334, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not beat those guys by one full body length in a 100m freestyle.\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those guys\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"one full body length\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"a 100m freestyle\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not humanly possible, okay?\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'So do not sell it to me, do not shove it down my throat.\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my throat\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not real.'\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking shortly after his astonishing win,Pan accused his rivals in the pool of 'looking down' on him and 'deliberately splashing' members of the Chinese coaching staff.\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2565, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8439604169322532, \"rank\": 0.17885133488409086, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his astonishing win\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"Pan\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"his rivals\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'On the first day, at the 4\\u00d7100 relay, after we finished swimming I greeted Chalmers.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first day\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4\\u00d7100 relay\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"Chalmers\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not pay me any attention at all,' Pan was reported as saying by The Telegraph.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2761, \"entities\": [], \"noun