 29 tests and never had a positive.\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"29 tests\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From May to July, I had 21 tests, no positive.\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3222}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"21 tests\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today we received a second test already.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a second test\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not think there has been any impact (on me) because all the testing has been done in the normal procedure \\u2026 So it's not a big issue.'\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any impact\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"all the testing\", \"from\": 3361, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"the normal procedure\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3414}, {\"ngram\": \"a big issue\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's anti-doping agency, Chinada, have repeatedly rejected accusations of cheating by their athletes, branding recent New York Times investigation 'extremely unfair and immoral'.\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3444, \"end\": 3449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8951886758544851, \"rank\": 0.11695834722223981, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 3565, \"end\": 3573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999998263997592, \"rank\": 1.6812829255136438e-07, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/N